26:30.173 --> 26:38.502
some cases, maybe they had a reason, because,

26:30.173 --> 26:38.502
well, I don't know. It was my observation that 
generally the Air Force types, Navy types, and

26:38.870 --> 27:04.519
what few Marine Corps types, you know, that came 
over there that were real gentlemen and knew what

26:38.870 --> 27:04.519
they were doing and knew the situation, they 
