they did, huh? See, of course, now you say when they 
come home, they were subject to induction and

27:29.767 --> 27:36.973
prescription and, I'm sure, come back to service.

27:38.894 --> 27:40.756
I can't remember exactly how many. You were too, 
weren't you? Right. Technically? Right. But see,

27:44.761 --> 27:48.405
had I gone to work for airlines, they wouldn't pay. 
