there, or in my diary. So five or six pilots out of 
how many? I'd say out of... That were left on the 4th

29:53.072 --> 30:01.963
of July.

30:02.023 --> 30:07.870
I'm guessing, I'd say four or five out of about, at 
that time,

30:12.423 --> 30:15.808
40, 45, see a lot of them had already gone home. Some 
of the pilots went home just before July 4th. They

30:19.975 --> 30:20.836
just had it. Well, they had it, yeah, and they knew 
they were good. And the old man people, they were in

