31:15.623 --> 31:18.726
And how many did you ever have full-strength, do 
you think? No, we never did have full-strength

31:19.006 --> 31:20.828
pilots. No, I know, but approximately how many did 
you ever have? I think probably 65. The last

31:26.313 --> 31:30.177
contingent was about the same as mine, around 35. 
