31:32.479 --> 31:36.463
and all... but five decided to go, four or five 
decided to go home. Yeah. Now, did you find that

31:42.600 --> 31:44.002
unusual? That all, that no one wanted to stay and 
continue the war effort? No, I didn't. As a matter

31:51.131 --> 31:56.778
of fact,

