34:08.401 --> 34:13.347
service,

34:08.401 --> 34:13.347
we'll get you ready. I think, I bet you there could 
have been as many as 25 or 30, let's say. I would say

34:18.113 --> 34:23.620
25 or 30. And a lot of the airmen, I think, see, You 
