34:25.936 --> 34:31.923
between a lot of the airmen and the pilots over 
there. We're a pilot state. I'm sure you can talk to

34:33.185 --> 34:35.027
airmen in the state. A lot of them in the state. But 
just like anything, it's like fire. It starts

34:38.331 --> 34:39.232
spreading. It keeps spreading like more and more. 
As the river gets around, I'm going home. Gee, if

34:43.797 --> 34:45.459
you go home, I'll go home. Something like that. 
Sure. Chain effect. Okay.

34:51.126 --> 34:51.727
Okay. Now, tell me about Doolittle. All I know 
about the Doolittle is, of course, we heard about

34:55.957 --> 35:00.462
it on the radio. Was it July of 42? June of 42? It had 
