April. April, I think. Because, matter of fact, we 
were still at Kunming when I met two of the pilots At

35:21.050 --> 35:26.535
the hostel one night, they had trickled down 
through the underground. I mean, Chinese picked

35:26.615 --> 35:29.898
them up, got them through the line. Some of them 
went down the line. A lot of them went down the line.

