37:17.791 --> 37:30.529
what was the impact that the Flying Tigers had on 
your life and your career?

37:34.194 --> 37:37.579
Well, I think perhaps it...

37:46.372 --> 37:47.393
I think it... served several purposes, one of 
which it seemed as though I had achieved some of my

37:49.651 --> 37:56.700
objectives. Sure. Two out of three. Yeah. Plus, 
not only that, but I had made money. I had become a

38:02.527 --> 38:03.689
hero. I was proud of what I'd done. And, you know, 
the American Federation album, there's a lot of

38:06.793 --> 38:10.477
other books. I was 19...

