the outstanding Texan in the Junior Chamber of 
Commerce in 1942 in Dallas, and that was quite an

38:19.486 --> 38:37.438
honor.

38:39.281 --> 38:43.148
I guess I bask in the glory and the heroism People 
wanted me to have a place. I got tired of that. You

