42:16.203 --> 42:22.289
combat record. I did all my combat

42:22.309 --> 42:33.019
in effect in China, and I have Chinese combat 
decorations and a British Distinguished Lion

42:22.309 --> 42:33.019
Cross. The top one there, the Air Force 
Distinguished Service medal in service. So, this

42:41.678 --> 42:45.825
being part of the Flying Tigers and that decision- 
