44:49.231 --> 45:09.095
The experiences that I had as

44:49.231 --> 45:09.095
a person,

44:49.231 --> 45:09.095
they had their imprint, probably too, on what's 
right and what's wrong, what's dangerous, what's

44:49.231 --> 45:09.095
not dangerous. I matured an awful lot in one year of 
combat. I think anybody does. I matured an awful

45:14.701 --> 45:17.685
lot.

45:22.019 --> 45:35.574
It definitely had a profound effect, I think, on my 
thinking, my

45:22.019 --> 45:35.574
advancement, my professional career. I was a 
professional far forehead of a lot of my buddies

45:35.594 --> 45:43.283
and cohorts. Okay, well, I think this is a good 
place to stop, and I want to start. Yeah, good.

