Tactics. And it was an organization where combat

46:30.881 --> 46:38.913
experienced people like myself had key 
positions. And the pilots themselves in the

46:39.895 --> 46:51.392
organization were combat experienced pilots to 
the extent they could get them at that stage of the

46:39.895 --> 46:51.392
war. And we brought cadres of, let's say, a new 
